                                    "Pierre_Instructions_Title": "How to Enter the Helmet Design Contest",
                                    "Pierre_Prize_Copy": "The grand prize winner will have their design featured on Pierre Gasly's helmet during the 2025 Australian Grand Prix, will receive a full-size, signed helmet, a local Grand Prix race day experience with a plus one, and virtually meet Pierre himself.",
                                    "Pierre_Prize_Title": "Win the Ultimate Fan Experience",
                                    "Pierre_Terms_Text": "For more information regarding the 2025 Pierre Gasly Helmet Design Competition, visit our dedicated [Terms \u0026 Conditions](https://www.%suffixOrigin%/%locale%/about-legal/2025-PierreGasly-Helmet-Design-Contest?utm_source=Partnerships\u0026utm_medium=landingpage\u0026utm_campaign=HelmetContest\u0026ref=GASLYHELM) page.",
