                                    "marinade-campaign-page-cta4": "Joined",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-disclaimer1": "Binance reserves the right in its sole discretion to amend or cancel this announcement at any time and for any reasons without prior notice.",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-disclaimer2": "Disclaimer:",
