                                    "marinade-campaign-page-reward": "Check $MNDE Rewards",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-reward-detail": "\u003cbr\u003e1.It may take up to **48 hours** for the system to display and update the estimated $MNDE rewards. You can track this on the Marinade Project page under the Yield+ section.\u003cbr\u003e 2.$MNDE rewards will be refreshed on a daily basis. However, any accumulated reward amount that falls **below 0.5 $MNDE** will not be displayed and distributed.\u003cbr\u003e 3.Please be aware that if $MSOL is either sold or transferred out, the accumulation of rewards will be halted immediately.",
