                                    "marinade-campaign-page-reward-dstribution-detail": "\u003cbr\u003e1.Rewards in $MNDE will be airdropped all at once **on the Solana chain** to your Binance Web3 Wallet before **2024-10-10 23:59 (UTC).**\u003cbr\u003e2.Any accumulated reward below **0.5 $MNDE** will not be distributed.\u003cbr\u003e3.$MSOL is a liquid staking token offering accumulated rewards. Its value progressively enhances over time, with the 7%+ APY return attached to be mirrored in its market value.",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-rule": "Campaign Rules",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-rule detail": "\u003cbr\u003e1.Only users who **sign up for this campaign** and complete the Quest above are eligible to receive rewards. \u003cbr\u003e 2.To qualify for rewards, the SOL staking amount must exceed an equivalent of **0.5 $MSOL**.\u003cbr\u003e3.Please be aware only **backed-up Binance MPC wallets** can participate in this campaign.\u003cbr\u003e4.The ultimate reward amount will be determined based on both the quantity of SOL staked in Marinade Liquid Staking Pool and the duration of $MSOL holdings.\u003cbr\u003e For reference, $MNDE rewards could be estimated using the following formula: \u003cbr\u003e$MNDE Reward Quantity = $MSOL Quantity * Integer Holding Days / 90",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-rule-detail": "\u003cbr\u003e1.Only users who **sign up for this campaign** and complete the Quest above are eligible to receive rewards. \u003cbr\u003e 2.To qualify for rewards, the SOL staking amount must exceed an equivalent of **0.5 $MSOL**.\u003cbr\u003e3.Please be aware only **backed-up Binance MPC wallets** can participate in this campaign.\u003cbr\u003e4.The ultimate reward amount will be determined based on both the quantity of SOL staked in Marinade Liquid Staking Pool and the duration of $MSOL holdings.\u003cbr\u003e For reference, $MNDE rewards could be estimated using the following formula: \u003cbr\u003e$MNDE Reward Quantity = $MSOL Quantity * Integer Holding Days / 90",
