                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.1": "Terms and Conditions:",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.10": "2.1. For all Binance Pay Users: All Binance Account holders (\"Pay Users\") who visit the Campaign landing page (or such other landing page as may be specified by us from time to time), log in to their account and send $0.001 equivalent virtual assets to “Official Nominees” or “Friends” will be eligible to receive one free red packet rewards(\" Red Packet\"). Each Red Packet consists of up to 100 USD worth of rewards in supported virtual assets. These Red Packets are limited, and will be distributed on a first-come, first-served basis.",
