                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.12": "2.3 There is up to 15 sends daily limits to \"Official Nominees\" and \"Friends\" collectively (e.g. 10 sends to Friends and 5 sends to Official Nominees max), subject to change which will be updated on the Campaign page. If you have used up the limit for the day:",
