                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.21": "(a) You can share the campaign activity link or poster with your friends through social media. The first 100,000 inviters will be eligible for the rewards stated on the Campaign page. You can check the status of the invites you have sent in the \"My Rewards \u003e Share Rewards\" section. Each invited user is eligible to receive only one invitation reward during the campaign period.",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.22": "3. Users are, under no circumstances, permitted to:",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.23": "(i) Create or use cheats, mods and/or hacks, or any other third-party software products that may change the result of the Binance Pay Send Campaign;",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.24": "(ii) Use software that allows the mining of data or otherwise intercepts or collects information in connection with the Binance Pay Send Campaign; and",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.25": "(iii) sell, buy or trade user accounts or impersonate any other individual in connection with user accounts, and the foregoing shall include all circumventions, similar actions or actions that produce an effect that matches the aforementioned prohibitions.",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.26": "(iv) Without limitation to any other rights or remedies that Binance may have under law, Binance may do any one or more of the following if Binance suspects or determines that You (whether alone or with others) have engaged in fraudulent, suspicious or unauthorized activity in connection with this Binance Pay Send Campaign (such activity referred to as “Fraud Action”):",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.27": "(a) Suspend or terminate your Binance account;",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.28": "(b) Disqualify You from this Campaign and claw back all points, entitlements and rewards issued by Binance in connection with the Fraud Action;",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.29": "4. Binance reserves the right at any time in its sole and absolute discretion to determine and/or amend or vary these terms without prior notice, including but not limited to canceling, extending, terminating or suspending this Campaign, its eligibility terms and criteria, the selection and number of winners, and the timing of any act to be done, and all users and participants shall be bound by these amendments. For clarity, Binance's decisions with respect to all aspects of this Campaign are final and non-appealable.",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.3": "1.1 These terms and conditions govern your participation in the Binance Pay Send Campaign organized by Binance Pay. By participating in the Binance Pay Send Campaign, you (“you” or “User”) agree unconditionally and irrevocably to be bound by, and shall be deemed to accept, these terms and conditions, and the following additional terms",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.30": "5. Risk reminder. Users confirm that they understand the risks involved in the trading or holding of digital assets (digital currencies, their derivatives or other types of digitalized assets with a certain value) and are recommended to exercise prudence and trade responsibly within their own capabilities. Binance does not take responsibility for any trading behaviours resulting in direct or indirect losses.",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.31": "6. Privacy. Participation to Binance Pay Send Campaign is limited to Binance Users who have expressly opted in to receive marketing communications from Binance. “Friends” and “Official Nominees” are only listed among these Binance Users who are eligible to participate in this campaign. Please note that “Friends” and “Official Nominees” can opt-out at any time and might not be eligible to be part of this campaign.",
                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.32": "Binance is committed to protecting your privacy. Your personal data will be handled in accordance with our Privacy Notice which is available at https://www.binance.com/en/privacy. By participating Binance Pay Send Campaign, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our Privacy Notice.",
