                                    "Pay.New.Send.Campaign.TnC.5": "all of which are incorporated by reference into these terms and conditions. If you do not agree to these terms and conditions, please do not access, participate in the Binance Pay Send Campaign. For the avoidance of doubt, capitalized terms used and not defined herein have the same meaning as given to such terms in the Binance Terms of Use.",
