                                    "SendGift_19": "7. Cancellations/refunds in respect of bookings and orders placed by you with the Service Provider directly via Send Gift Feature in Binance Pay, if any, will also be governed by the applicable terms and conditions between you and Service Provider. We have no role in governing refund/cancellation charges. The Service Provider is solely responsible for the content/goods/services made available by it to you directly, and you should contact the respective Service Provider directly in relation to the above mentioned queries. You may also raise your dispute (or any queries relating to Service Provider’s CS channel) for our onward notification to third party Service Provider, who in turn, shall be responsible for resolving your disputes or queries.",
