                                    "SendGift_24": "10. As the TPS is provided by third party Service Providers, you acknowledge and agree that we shall have no responsibility or liability to you whatsoever in respect of the TPS, its quality, performance and availability.",
                                    "SendGift_25": "11. You further understand and agree that we will not be liable for any losses or damages arising out of or relating to: (a) any inaccuracy, defect or omission of cryptocurrency price data; (b) any error or delay in the transmission of such data or the processing of your purchase order from Service Provider; (c) interruption in any such data; (d) regular or unscheduled maintenance carried out by us and/or our other partners (including Service Providers) in the provision of Send Gift Features or TPS to you (as the case may be), and service interruption and change resulting from such maintenance; (e) any damages incurred by other users’ actions, omissions or violation of these terms; (f) any damage caused by illegal actions of other third parties or actions that are not authorized by us; and (g) other exemptions mentioned in disclaimers and platform rules issued by us.",
                                    "SendGift_26": "12. These Send Gift Terms govern the relationship between you and us. Your dealings with the Service Providers , are solely between you and the relevant Service Provider. We have no liability to you in relation to any Service Provider (including any content, goods or services provided by such Service Provider as part of the Send Gift Feature) INDEMNITY",
                                    "SendGift_27": "13. You agree to indemnify us and to hold us harmless from and against any claims, actions, proceedings, investigations, demands, suits, costs, expenses and damages (including attorneys’ fees, fines or penalties imposed by any regulatory authority) arising out of or related to your use of, or conduct in connection with, your purchase, receipt of and access to TPS from the Service Provider. For clarity, this right of indemnification is in addition to the rights and protections afforded to us under the Binance Terms and Binance Pay Terms of Use (if applicable).",
                                    "SendGift_28": "PRIVACY",
                                    "SendGift_29": "14. You shall be bound by all the terms set out in the Binance Privacy Policy, which shall be read together with and supplemental to these Send Gift Terms. You additionally acknowledge and agree that: (a) all data provided by you into the Service Provider in Binance App platform, are collected and processed entirely by Service Provider, and such collection and processing of your data by Service Provider shall be governed by the applicable terms between you and Service Provider (including but not limited to the Service Provider’s own privacy policies, if any). We do not have access to or collect the data that you provide to Service Provider directly; (b) we may share information that you provide to us, with our service providers (including but not limited to the Service Providers as defined herein), if our service providers require such information for legal and regulatory compliance purposes, or as part of service delivery to you. In such an event, we will request your express consent to do so, and the processing of your data will be in accordance with our Binance Privacy Policy; and (c) if supported by the mini-program functionalities, the Service Provider may also send you push-notifications, via the Binance App platform.",
                                    "SendGift_3": "Terms of Use",
                                    "SendGift_30": "GENERAL",
                                    "SendGift_31": "15. You shall be also bound by all the terms set out in the Binance Terms and Binance Pay Terms of Use (if applicable), which shall be read together with and supplemental to these Send Gift Terms. Accordingly, the rights and protections afforded to us under the Binance Terms and Binance Pay Terms of Use (if applicable) shall equally apply and be additional to the rights and protections afforded to us under these Send Gift Terms.",
