                                    "SendGift_6": "This Send Gift Feature is a service made available to you through Binance App. It allows you to connect with third party service providers (“Service Providers\") to purchase goods or services directly from such Service Providers using Binance App.  Depending on which  Third Party Service you purchase goods or services (“TPS”) from, additional Third Party Service specific terms (if any) may also apply.",
                                    "SendGift_7": "These terms, and the additional TPS specific terms if any (collectively, “Send Gift Terms”), are concluded and constitute a legally binding agreement between you (the user of Send Gift Feature in Binance App)  (referred to as \"you\"), and the respective Binance Operator(s) (as defined in the Binance Terms, referred to jointly as \"we\", or \" us\").",
                                    "SendGift_8": "Please read these Send Gift Terms carefully as they govern your access to and use of the Send Gift Feature. If you do not agree to these Send Gift Terms or any other terms that are incorporated by reference herein (all of which, may be amended from time to time without further notice), please cease access immediately and do not continue to use the Send Gift Feature in Binance App.",
                                    "SendGift_9": "For clarity, your continued access to and use of Send Gift P Feature shall constitute your acceptance of these Send Gift Terms and all other terms that are incorporated herein, including any updates or modifications to them from time to time.",
                                    "Simple-earn-copy": "Simple Earn products are principal-protected, providing you with a secure way to earn rewards through either flexible or locked terms and allowing you to earn benefits without compromising your initial investment.",
                                    "Simple-earn-title": "Simple Earn",
                                    "WB-Disclaimer1": "Have more questions? Check out our Affiliate Program Guide for additional answers. All affiliate members agree to be bound by and to accept the Affiliate Program Standard Terms and Conditions.",
                                    "WB-Disclaimer2": "Disclaimer: Binance reserves the right to disqualify users from participating in the Affiliate Program and revoke any commissions from users who engage in dishonest or abusive activities to earn commissions. This includes bulk-account registrations to obtain additional bonuses, using “phishing” websites containing referral links, posting referral links as advertisements on search engines, and any other activity concerning unlawful, fraudulent, or harmful purposes.\nEffective September 19, 2024, the $100 USD trading fee voucher obtained through the Referral Mode will no longer be applicable for API trading.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-ANS6": "- Your account failed to meet the registration requirements.\n- Unfortunately, it is in breach of our terms and conditions, and therefore, we cannot approve your request.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans1": "To qualify for the welcome bonus, new users must be referred by an affiliate who has signed up for the welcome bonus package. Please ensure you refer users using your ‘Referral Pro’ link/ID.\n\nOnce a user signs up through a registered affiliate’s referral link, they will automatically receive 3-6 tasks to complete in the Task Center. If you sign up through this page without using a registered affiliate’s referral link, you will not receive the welcome bonus tasks. \n\nPlease verify that you are using the referral link of a registered Binance Affiliate before signing up for this promotion.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans2": "Every Binance affiliate is eligible to offer this promotion to their audience. Affiliates can use their ‘Referral Pro’ link/ID to invite users. Invitees will receive rewards ranging from $100 (default for all) to higher tiers depending on your affiliate performance. \n\nIf you are a Binance Affiliate and your new users do not receive their tasks even after using your Referral Link, please reach out to your Local Affiliate Manager.\n\nAvailable Packages:\n\n-$100 Package (Default)\n\n-$300 Package\n \n- Requires 20 newly-registered referrals in the past 30 days (excluding batch registrations).\n\n-$600 Package**\n  - Requires 200 newly-registered referrals in the past 30 days (excluding batch registrations).\n\n\n[Upgrade](https://www.binance.com/en/survey/f9aefc4f71294b47815d79a2ec59ddb5)  your package to offer higher rewards to your referrals and attract more users!",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans3": "Yes, every Binance affiliate is eligible to offer this promotion to their audience. Each affiliate in this campaign has a unique referral link with an embedded welcome bonus package, ranging from $100 (default to all) to higher tiers depending on your affiliate performance. If you are a Binance Affiliate and your new users do not receive their tasks even if using your Referral Link, please reach out to your Local Affiliate manager.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans4": "To view and complete tasks, click on your Account icon and select “Task Center” from the drop-down menu or your dashboard after logging in. Alternatively, you can directly visit the Task Center or access it via the “Account” or “More” menu on your Binance App.\n\nBasic $100 Package Tasks:\n1. Complete KYC: Receive a $20 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n2. First-time Deposit of More Than $10: Receive a $30 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n3. First-time Trade of More Than $10:Receive a $50 trading fee rebate voucher.\n\nTier 2 $300 Package Tasks:\n-Spot Packages:\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $5,000 within 7 days: Receive a $200 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n- Spot + Futures Packages:\n  - Futures trade of ≥ $10,000 within 7 days: Receive a $50 futures trading fee rebate voucher.\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $3,000 within 7 days: Receive a $100 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n\nTier 3 $600 Package Tasks:\n- Spot Packages:\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $5,000 within 7 days: Receive a $200 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $50,000 within 7 days: Receive a $300 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n- Spot + Futures Packages:\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $5,000 within 7 days: Receive a $200 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n  - Spot trade of ≥ $3,000 within 7 days: Receive a $100 spot trading fee rebate voucher.\n  - Futures trade of ≥ $10,000 within 7 days: Receive a $50 futures trading fee rebate voucher.\n  - Futures trade of ≥ $1,000,000 within 7 days: Receive a $150 futures trading fee rebate voucher.\n\nImportant Note:\nInvitees who register via ‘Referral’ mode will not be eligible for package tasks.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans5": "Click on your Account icon and select “Reward Hub” from the drop-down menu or in your dashboard after logging in to your account. Alternatively, you can directly visit [here](https://www.binance.com/en/my/coupon) or access the Reward Hub via the “Account” or “More” menu on your Binance App.",
                                    "WB-FAQ-Ans7": "Yes, the reward structure or voucher structure for the welcome package may be subject to change. Binance reserves the right to modify the welcome bonus package or terminate the welcome bonus program without prior notice.",
