                                    "marinade-campaign-page-MSOL": "What is $MSOL？",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-MSOL-detail": "$MSOL is a liquid staking token that you receive when you stake SOL on the Marinade protocol. These $MSOL tokens represent your staked SOL tokens in Marinade's stake pool. $MSOL is a rewards-accruing liquid staking token. This means that after each Solana epoch (2-3 days), its value is recalculated based on the staking rewards earned by the Marinade Stake Pool.\u003cbr\u003e[Read More](https://www.binance.com/bapi/mp/v1/public/link/redirect/web3?url=aHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLm1hcmluYWRlLmZpbmFuY2UvZ2V0dGluZy1zdGFydGVkL3doYXQtaXMtbXNvbA)",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-Marinade": "What is Marinade Protocol?",
