                                    "marinade-campaign-page-quest": "Quest: Participate in SOL Liquid Staking with Marinade to Earn Bonus $MNDE Airdrop",
                                    "marinade-campaign-page-quest details": "**Steps:**\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e1.Log into Binance Web3 Wallet and click [Join Now] on the campaign page\u003cbr\u003e2.Click [Complete Now] and navigate to the Marinade Liquid Staking Pool\u003cbr\u003e3.Input **at least 0.5 $MSOL** equivalent of staking amount, confirm priority fee, then click [Stake]\u003cbr\u003eThe accumulated $MNDE rewards below 0.5 $MNDE will not be distributed.\u003cbr\u003e4.Once staked successfully, you'll receive $MSOL. This amount will be shown on both your Binance Web3 Wallet homepage and the Marinade Liquid Staking Pool page\u003cbr\u003e[ Tutorial \u0026gt;](https://www.binance.com/en/support/faq/b85d0b910b4d42fcac720a946db75c7a)",
